_sText:
After around a month in the making I present to you jb_tellexx!

A map based on/inspired by the band I Don't Know How But They Found Me!

It features many songs and games including mancannon, sweeper, dodgeball, colours, 4 couches and more!

THIS IS THE FINAL VERSION. THERE WILL BE NO MORE WORK DONE ON THIS MAP!

Hope you enjoy!
